            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[感冒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_ganmao-286fc59b6d.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%BF%87%E6%95%8F%E4%BD%93%E8%B4%A8%E8%A6%81%E8%AD%A6%E6%83%95%E5%92%B3%E5%97%BD%E5%8F%98%E5%BC%82%E6%80%A7%E5%93%AE%E5%96%98%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%BF%87%E6%95%8F%E4%BD%93%E8%B4%A8%E8%A6%81%E8%AD%A6%E6%83%95%E5%92%B3%E5%97%BD%E5%8F%98%E5%BC%82%E6%80%A7%E5%93%AE%E5%96%98%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#过敏体质要警惕咳嗽变异性哮喘#</span></a>】春季过敏易引发“咳嗽变异性哮喘”。这类哮喘通常以干咳为主，夜间咳嗽是重要特征，因此又称为“不喘的哮喘”。一般感冒咳嗽只持续几天，但咳嗽变异性哮喘会持续咳嗽两周以上，若延误诊治则可能发展为典型哮喘。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%A4%9C%E9%97%B4%E5%8F%8D%E5%A4%8D%E5%92%B3%E5%97%BD%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E7%89%B9%E6%AE%8A%E5%93%AE%E5%96%98%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%A4%9C%E9%97%B4%E5%8F%8D%E5%A4%8D%E5%92%B3%E5%97%BD%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E7%89%B9%E6%AE%8A%E5%93%AE%E5%96%98%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#夜间反复咳嗽可能是一种特殊哮喘#</span></a> <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4879832782405640" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hc1e6r8k2aj60rk0fiqbt02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/MU5yGVjTlx083UgQCSb601041200U0iw0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1BThihd3VLAY5R&amp;Expires=1679030248&amp;ssig=%2FihtQZGsd1&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/oxWTUHxXlx083UgPSxiM01041200twRq0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template